-- Spain Studies Scrapping Tax Deductions in Budget, El Pais Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-03-18T12:12:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-18/spain-studies-scrapping-tax-deductions-in-budget-el-pais-says.html
Spain ’s ruling  People’s Party  is
studying scrapping some tax deductions and accelerating payments
in preparation for the 2012 budget to be presented March 30,  El
Pais  said, citing unnamed officials at the Budget Ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
